includedAssets.title: Rio Movie
includedAssets.synopsis: Domesticated macaw Blu (Jesse Eisenberg) travels to Rio de Janeiro with the bird of his dreams, the free-spirited Jewel (Anne Hathaway). Together they dodge an evil cockatoo (Jermaine Clement) and try to understand their Amazon roots. Hit family animation and its sequel from the makers of Ice Age.
